ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://bisonggallery.com/wp-content/uploads/2026
 /04/att.Saw2UK1wv2od8mEJLrNsCGRmY_Gk9E0A7Pb-YxO_RWY.jpeg
UID:T73shRegRtdzJCEmGgnbr
SUMMARY:Jubilee : A Celebration of Freedom
DTSTAMP:20260620T142401Z
DTSTART:20260619T170000Z
DESCRIPTION:June 19\, 2026 Opening reception at Bisong Art Gallery 5 – 8pm\
	n\nExhibition Dates: June 19 – July 25\, 2026\nExhibition Venue: Bisong Ar
	t Gallery\nGallery Hours: Thursday – Saturday from 1 – 5pm\n\nGroup Art Ex
	hibition: The concept of freedom has been a fundamental aspect of human ex
	istence since the beginning of time. It is a complex and multifaceted idea
	 that has inspired countless artists throughout history. An art exhibition
	 representing the meaning of freedom is an opportunity to explore the many
	 different ways in which this concept can be expressed and interpreted.\n\
	n\nThe D.R.E.A.M Affect Foundation’s mission is raising awareness of the u
	nderrepresentation  of art students of color in higher learning institutio
	ns. We believe that every individual has the right to pursue their passion
	 and creativity\, regardless of their background.  Our goal is to create a
	 platform for discussion and collaboration among students\, educators\, an
	d institutions to address the systemic barriers that prevent minority stud
	ents from accessing opportunities in the arts.  We aim to empower and supp
	ort these students in their pursuit of higher education\, and to work towa
	rds a diverse and inclusive arts community.  We believe that by amplifying
	 the voices of underrepresented art students\, we can create meaningful ch
	ange and promote an equitable society. Keeping in step with our mission\, 
	The D.R.E.A.M. Affect Foundation will be donating a portion of all art sal
	es to scholarships for minority art students.\n\nJubilee: A Celebration of
	 Freedom. The concept of freedom has been a fundamental aspect  of human e
	xistence since the beginning of time. It is a complex and multifaceted ide
	a that  has inspired countless artists throughout history. An art exhibiti
	on representing the meaning  of freedom is an opportunity to explore the m
	any different ways in which these concepts can be  expressed and interpret
	ed.\n\nhttps://bisonggallery.com/event/jubilee-a-celebration-of-freedom-2/
	\n\nFrom Bisong Art Gallery
URL:https://bisonggallery.com/event/jubilee-a-celebration-of-freedom-2/
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:bisong-art-gallery
CATEGORIES:Bisong Art Gallery
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT3H
END:VEVENT
