	a 90-minute tour with a local historian. Your guide will share stories of 
	the Allen brothers and provide historical information about the people\, p
	laces\, and events along the bayou that helped shape Houston. \n  \nCost \
	n\nAdults: $40\nChildren: $32 (ages 4-12)\n\n  \nDeparture Location\nAllen
	’s Landing (1019 Commerce St.) \nWeather permitting. Reservations Required
